  Requirements:
    php 5.2.1 or later
    MySQL 5.0 or later (for stored procedures and the like)
    A web browser - currently tested under Safari 2.0-3.1 and FireFox 2

  Summary:
    Web based MySQL Stored Procedure, Function and Trigger Management. 
    Written in PHP and Javascript, this Ajax application is the perfect 
    companion to phpMyAdmin. Includes command line interface & other special features.

  Download:
    Source is available at both phpmyide.com and SourceForge, project 
    is named, cleverly, phpMyIDE.

  Credits:
